  --/|Script Name : Sleep
  --/|Version     : 2.0
  --/|Modified By : Farsidegallery
  --/|  
  --/|  Script checks for spell level used and makes sure the slot is available. Script will find creatures in range and rolls saving throw.
  --/|  Script applies sleep condition to those that fail in order of current HP ensuring to stay below total number of points
  --/|  rolled and plays visual effect. It will deduct 1 spell slot from the appropriate level.
  --/|
  
