  --&SleepLink|https://files.d20.io/images/466452653/fWh2Z4z8OtwxGOeorsnMCQ/med.webm?1764800273
  
  --/| Place the name and URL of your spell target token here.
  --&SpellTargetToken|Spell Token
  --&URLlink|https://files.d20.io/images/469753332/ew1SU1DcQK4eborJlOqNQw/original.png
  
  --/|Button Format
  --#buttonBackground|#4d1635
  --#buttonFontFace|Tahoma
  --#buttonFontSize|14px
  
  --#noMinMaxHighlight|1
  
